Don't Let Your Pet Become a Statistic
¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤ More than 10 million pets are lost each year said by ASPCA. A microchip is simply NOT enough. ¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤¤
Tagg gives you the power of GPS to locate your pet at any time. A microchip does not alert you if your pet is lost, or show you their location, but Tagg does.
